<h1><center>TIC-TAC-TOE using ASP.NET</center></h1>
<h2>Objective</h2>
<p>Develop a web-based Tic-Tac-Toe game using ASP.NET Core 8 or 9 with Razor Pages or MVC, ensuring a fully interactive and dynamic gameplay experience.</p>

<h2>Learning Outcome</h2>
<p>
   * By completing this lab, students will:

   * Gain hands-on experience with ASP.NET Core 8 or 9.

   * Understand how to handle state management in a web application.

   * Utilize Razor Pages or MVC to build an interactive web application.

   * Implement real-time interactions using SignalR (optional for multiplayer mode).
</p>

